import React, { Component } from 'react'
// import 'font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css';
import { Container, Footer } from 'mdbreact';
import '../App.css';
class FooterComp extends Component {
    render() {
        return ( <
            Footer color = "stylish-color-dark"
            className = "page-footer font-small pt-4 mt-4"
            className = 'footer'
            className = "footer" >


            <
            div className = "text-center" >
            <
            ul className = "list-unstyled list-inline" >
            <
            li className = "list-inline-item" > < a className = "btn-floating btn-sm btn-fb mx-1"
            href = "https://www.facebook.com/"
            target = "_blank" > < i className = "fa fa-facebook" > < /i></a > < /li> <
            li className = "list-inline-item" > < a className = "btn-floating btn-sm btn-tw mx-1"
            href = "https://github.com/serkansonmez06"
            target = "_blank" > < i className = "fa fa-github" > < /i></a > < /li> <
            li className = "list-inline-item" > < a className = "btn-floating btn-sm btn-gplus mx-1" > < i className = "fa fa-google"
            href = "https://www.google.com/ "
            target = "_blank" > < /i></a > < /li> <
            li className = "list-inline-item" > < a className = "btn-floating btn-sm btn-li mx-1"
            href = "https://www.linkedin.com/in/serkan-sonmez-mba/"
            target = "_blank" > < i className = "fa fa-linkedin" > < /i></a > < /li>

            <
            /ul> <
            /div> <
            div className = "footer-copyright text-center" >
            <
            Container fluid >
            <
            span > & copy; {
                (new Date().getFullYear()) }
            Copyright: Capture the Image Inc. < /span> <
            /Container> <
            /div> <
            /Footer>

        )
    }
}
export default FooterComp
